lines: THEY BROUGHT THEIR GIFTS TO JESUS
Ba ka leta zipego zyabo kuli Jesu,
Jesu wa tambula luyando lwabo lonse,
Milimo mibotu a ku gwasya bacete,
Jesu wa zi yanda zipego zyabo zyonse.
Sena u yanda ku mu letela nca yanda,
Ko mwambila, Mwami nda ku pa moyo wangu.
Ambali kwa bapi kwa ka imvwi mucete,
Wa bona zipego zyabo zyonse zibotu,
Elyo wa ku yanda ku tola cipego,
Pesi kunyina nca jisi ku mu tolela.
Wa lila ÒMwami ndi ku zyi u li syiluse,
Ko tolankwe ndi jisi, moyo wangu mubi,Ó
Jesu wa mwambila uta ciiti ncisyonto
Zyonse nzibotu pesi cako ci la inda.
